The '''87th Academy Awards''' ceremony, presented by the [[Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] (AMPAS), will honor the best [[2014 in film|films of 2014]] and will take place February 22, 2015, at the [[Dolby Theatre]] in [[Hollywood]], [[Los Angeles]] beginning at 5:30&nbsp;p.m.&nbsp;[[Pacific Time Zone|PST]] (8:30&nbsp;p.m.&nbsp;[[Eastern Time Zone|EST]]/01:30&nbsp;[[Coordinated Universal Time|UTC]]).<ref>{{cite news|title=The Academy Selects 2014 and 2015 Show Dates|url=https://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2013/20130325.html|work=The Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|accessdate=May 6, 2014}}</ref> During the ceremony, the Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences will present [[Academy Award]]s (commonly referred to as Oscars) in 24 categories. The ceremony, televised in the United States by [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]], will be produced by [[Neil Meron]] and [[Craig Zadan]] and directed by [[Hamish Hamilton (director)|Hamish Hamilton]]. Actor [[Neil Patrick Harris]] is scheduled to host the ceremony for the first time.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Gray|first1=Tim|title=Neil Patrick Harris to Host the Oscars|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/neil-patrick-harris-to-host-the-oscars-exclusive-1201312943/|accessdate=October 15, 2014|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=October 15, 2014}}</ref>

In related events, the Academy held its 6th annual [[Governors Awards]] ceremony at the Grand Ballroom of the [[Hollywood and Highland Center]] on November 8, 2014.<ref name="Governors">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/academy-unveils-2014-governor-awards-recipients-1201289156/ |title=Academy Unveils 2014 Governors Awards Recipients |accessdate=September 1, 2014 |work=Variety}}</ref> On February 7, 2015, in a ceremony at [[The Beverly Hills Hotel]] in [[Beverly Hills, California]], the [[Academy Award for Technical Achievement|Academy Awards for Technical Achievement]] were presented by hosts [[Margot Robbie]] and [[Miles Teller]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2015/01/28/margot-robbie-miles-teller-to-hand-out-sci-tech-oscars/|title=Margot Robbie, Miles Teller to hand out Sci-Tech Oscars|accessdate=January 29, 2015|publisher=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|date=January 28, 2015}}</ref>

